31:58.999 --> 32:01.032
My aim.

32:01.034 --> 32:03.569
She engaged in
the outside world,

32:03.571 --> 32:05.705
she became extremely popular,

32:05.707 --> 32:07.907
she even fell in love.

32:07.909 --> 32:11.209
Not to toot my own
